snippet.title: Overwatch 2 - Free to Play Trailer - Xbox & Bethesda Games Showcase 2022
snippet.description: Overwatch 2 arrives on October 4 as an always on, free to play experience featuring brand new content. Learn more at the Reveal Event on June 16 at 10 AM PT, streaming on Overwatch’s official Twitch and Youtube channels.
